sequenceDiagram
    participant RSS as RSS Feeds
    participant BE as Cloud Run Backend
    participant FS as Firestore /reports
    participant APP as Android App
    participant ROOM as Room DB
    participant UI as Compose UI
    participant GPS as Device GPS
    participant FCM as FCM

    Note over RSS,FCM: 🔄 Continuous Scrape Cycle

    RSS->>BE: RSS feed articles (XML)
    BE->>BE: Keyword classify disease & severity
    BE->>BE: Geocode location → lat/lon
    BE->>FS: Write OutbreakReport document

    Note over FS,UI: 📡 Real-Time Sync to App

    FS-->>APP: Firestore snapshot listener fires
    APP->>APP: documentToEntity() mapping
    APP->>ROOM: dao.insertAll(entities)
    ROOM-->>UI: getCachedFeed() Flow emits
    UI->>UI: Render feed cards / map pins / charts

    Note over GPS,UI: 📍 Proximity Alert Flow

    GPS->>APP: Location update (lat/lon)
    APP->>ROOM: getAllReports()
    loop For each cached report
        APP->>APP: Haversine distance check
        alt distance < 15km
            APP->>UI: Show ghost_alert banner
            APP->>FCM: Trigger local notification
        end
    end

    Note over APP,FS: 👤 User Auth & Social Flow

    APP->>FS: Firebase Auth sign-in
    FS-->>APP: auth state change
    APP->>FS: Read /users/{uid}
    APP->>FS: Listen /chats & /direct_chats
    FS-->>UI: Real-time message updates

    Note over APP,BE: 🔁 Manual Refresh Flow

    UI->>APP: User taps Refresh button
    APP->>BE: POST /trigger-job (Bearer JWT)
    BE->>RSS: Fetch latest feeds
    BE->>FS: Write new reports
    FS-->>APP: Snapshot listener fires (loop above)
